### Swagger UI
GET https://localhost/swagger-ui/index.html

### 1. Create a Project
POST https://localhost/projects
Accept: application/json

> {%
  client.global.set("projectId", response.body.projectId);
%}

### 2. Picture Generation Task
POST https://localhost/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "task": "Generate a picture of an apple."
}

> {%
  client.global.set("taskExecutionId", response.body.taskExecutionId);
%}

### 3. Start SSE connection (subscribe to events)
# Note: This is the SSE endpoint that will stream events for your task execution
GET https://localhost/task-executions/{{taskExecutionId}}/events
Accept: text/event-stream

### 3. Get all events for a task execution (JSON)
GET https://localhost/task-executions/{{taskExecutionId}}/events
Accept: application/json

### 4. Get task execution state
GET https://localhost/task-executions/{{taskExecutionId}}/state
Accept: application/json

### 5. Get all logs for a project
GET https://localhost/projects/{{projectId}}/logs
Accept: text/plain

